Get known for scheduling time, as in, whenever ANYone asks you to do anything unscheduled, say, &quot;hm, no, sorry, i can't do that right now, can we pencil it in at xxxx (where xxxx is some time later), i've scheduled THIS time with 5 (or 10 or 40) other people online at the moment&quot;  Do this whether you are playing everquest or not.<br>
